  CustomStringTableItem "{68FB0001A00000C6}" {
   Id "CRX_EAI_T-GlbRearmType_Desc"
   Target_en_us "Set global rearm type of how AI character(s) should be allowed to rearm. Note: None = No rearm | Default: Enemy and friendly weapons and magazines | Weapons: Friendly weapons and magazines only | Magazines: Magazines of the same original ( weapon/magazine ) type only."
